          <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-12">
              <h3>Please read the instructions carefully before proceeding to the quiz:</h3>
              <hr>
              <div>
                <ul>
                  <li>You must register with your NITH email id only.</li>
                  <li>The quiz contains 10 sections . Each section consist of 4 questions each. </li>
                  <li>A single textbox is present at the end of each section. You must write your answers in the textbox separated by a single space.</li>
                  <li>There shouldn't be any leading or following space in the answer string.</li>
                  <li>For a valid submission you must give the answers to all the 4 questions.</li>
                  <li>The aim is to compute the answers before anybody else does. So if any player makes a correct submission you would be directed to the next section.</li>
                  <li>The latest submission is recorded on a blockchain. You can view the CryptoBoard at any time to view the details and points of players who have answered the questions.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <button id="openQuiz2" class="s2button my-4">Start Quiz</button>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</section>

